data.content:
Anh - Anh
decor
['deɪkɔ:, 'dɛ-]
■ noun
1》 the furnishing and decoration of a room.
2》 stage scenery.
Origin
C19: from Fr. décor, from décorer, from L. decorare (see decorate).

Từ điển Đồng nghĩa
decor
▸ noun DECORATION, furnishing, ornamentation; colour scheme.

Từ điển Kỹ thuật (EN)
Lĩnh vực: xây dựng
■ việc dàn cảnh
architectural decor
■ trang trí kiến trúc
sculptural decor
■ tượng trang trí

sentences.en: Each December, Vietnamese organizations for people with disabilities hold a joint celebration in honor of World AIDS Day (Dec.1), International Day of Disabled Persons (Dec. 3) and International Volunteers’ Day (Dec. 5).
